1. *Planine* su izvor energije za čitav svet. (Mountains are a source of energy for the whole world.)

2. On se penje po *planinama* ceo svoj život. (He has been climbing mountains his whole life.)

3. Putovanje na *planinama* je nezaboravno iskustvo. (Traveling in the mountains is an unforgettable experience.)

4. *Planinama* pruža se prekrasan pogled. (The mountains offer a beautiful view.)

5. *Planinama* vladaju jaka vjetrovi. (Strong winds rule the mountains.)

6. *Planinama* vladaju hladnoća i tišina. (The mountains are ruled by cold and silence.)